<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="About GitOps App - Architecture and components">
  <title><%= title %> - GitOps App</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="header">
    <nav class="nav container">
      <a href="/" class="nav-brand" aria-label="GitOps App Home">
        <svg class="logo" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
          <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/>
          <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
        </svg>
        <span class="brand-text">GitOps App</span>
      </a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about" class="nav-link active">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="/metrics" class="nav-link">Metrics</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="about-content">
    <section class="about-section">
      <h1>About GitOps App</h1>
      <p>
        This application demonstrates a complete GitOps workflow for deploying and managing 
        infrastructure and applications. The entire platform is built on Proxmox VE using 
        Terraform for infrastructure provisioning, GitLab CI/CD for automated deployments, 
        and Prometheus/Grafana for observability.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Architecture Overview</h2>
      <p>
        The platform consists of four isolated virtual machines, each with a specific role:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>App VM (gitops-app):</strong> Runs the Node.js/Express web application on port 3000. Serves the home page, about page, and Prometheus metrics endpoint.</li>
        <li><strong>DB VM (gitops-db):</strong> Hosts PostgreSQL 15 database with the <code>gitopsdb</code> database. Accessible on port 5432.</li>
        <li><strong>Monitoring VM (gitops-monitoring):</strong> Runs Prometheus, Grafana, and Node Exporter via Docker Compose. Provides metrics collection, dashboards, and alerting.</li>
        <li><strong>Runner VM (gitops-runner):</strong> GitLab Runner with Docker executor for running CI/CD pipelines.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Infrastructure:</strong> Proxmox VE 8, Terraform 1.5+, bpg/proxmox provider</li>
        <li><strong>Application:</strong> Node.js 18, Express 4, EJS templating</li>
        <li><strong>Database:</strong> PostgreSQL 15</li>
        <li><strong>CI/CD:</strong> GitLab CI/CD with Docker executor</li>
        <li><strong>Monitoring:</strong> Prometheus 2.47+, Grafana 10+, Node Exporter</li>
        <li><strong>Containerization:</strong> Docker 20.10+, Docker Compose v2</li>
        <li><strong>OS:</strong> Debian 12 (Bookworm) on all VMs</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>GitOps Workflow</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Infrastructure Changes:</strong> Modify Terraform files → Commit to Git → GitLab CI runs <code>terraform plan</code> → Manual approval → <code>terraform apply</code></li>
        <li><strong>Application Changes:</strong> Modify application code → Create Merge Request → CI runs tests → Merge to main → CD pipeline deploys via rsync → Systemd restarts service</li>
        <li><strong>Monitoring Updates:</strong> Update Prometheus rules or Grafana dashboards → Commit → Manual trigger deploys new Docker Compose stack</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Network & Security</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>All VMs on the same bridge network (vmbr0) with DHCP</li>
        <li>QEMU Guest Agent enabled for IP discovery</li>
        <li>SSH key-based authentication only (no passwords)</li>
        <li>PostgreSQL configured for MD5 authentication from all IPs</li>
        <li>Grafana secured with admin/admin (change in production!)</li>
        <li>Prometheus metrics exposed on /metrics endpoints</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Access URLs</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>App:</strong> http://192.168.8.189:3000</li>
        <li><strong>About Page:</strong> http://192.168.8.189:3000/about</li>
        <li><strong>Metrics:</strong> http://192.168.8.189:3000/metrics</li>
        <li><strong>Grafana:</strong> http://192.168.8.190:3000 (admin/admin)</li>
        <li><strong>Prometheus:</strong> http://192.168.8.190:9090</li>
        <li><strong>PostgreSQL:</strong> 192.168.8.188:5432 (db: gitopsdb, user: gitopsapp)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">← Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>GitOps App - Deployed with <span class="heart">♥</span> via GitOps on Proxmox VE</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>